&lt;p>A simple, no-framework Go backend.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Backend development is typically interface-driven, or, as some say, CRUD engineering. This article will use Go to show how to read data from a database and return JSON.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="database">Database
